{"tid":927743,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知咩事比人回頭望","createTime":"2018-12-04T11:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-18T04:48:02.000Z","uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ec2494b56ac61d632286720d30fea05deb878482","tid":927743,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:03:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我一個人行，咁岩前面有3條友仔，一肥一瘦就係度開心吹水<br />\n<br />\n因為條路窄，咁三條友一字排開，我做唔到拓海哥咁既速度甩開佢地。。。<br />\n<br />\n咁就左面條瘦閪無啦啦寧轉頭望左我一眼，利申返，小弟用緊正常步速行住去餐廳搵食，應該唔會係jojo咁撚樣。。。<br />\n<br />\n條友望完之後同個肥閪吱吱噚左幾句，個肥既聽完都望左我一下。。。然後兩條友唔知up乜尻。。。佢3個繼續人行路上一字頂9住條路，直至彎位終於分道揚鑣。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔通。。。我個樣柒左咁多?定佢3個係基佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3001155e76dc83ca2664e9a4305517eacc1f7745","tid":927743,"uid":129660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:08:10.000Z","msg":"樓豬都幾唔得閒"},{"pid":"a03b0b7d38eeefbb2c850977986659fa3e7fe404","tid":927743,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3001155e76dc83ca2664e9a4305517eacc1f7745","tid":927743,"uid":129660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:08:10.000Z","msg":"樓豬都幾唔得閒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:10:46.000Z","msg":"我褲連都拉好 望乜尻先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72fc583ff84f5406c8214b1a9198ea5320f7f48","tid":927743,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T11:15:38.000Z","msg":"形容下衣著，三個都毒撚款 揹住個書包<br />\n著住大褸，長褲<br />\n6點幾今日仲要30度咁都唔除褸<br />\n個款唔似住附近或返工<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會係d絕症患者，定要報驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84cae3dca20ec4f20291f5f5c63a5e738e25d999","tid":927743,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c72fc583ff84f5406c8214b1a9198ea5320f7f48"